-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Sencha Touch 2.0 Mobile Enterprise App Example
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

OSS project intended to be a 'Fully Functional Real-World Enterprise Example'

Similar to Sencha 'KitchenSink' - but geared towards Enterprise needs.

Since I need to do this for my project anyways - why not share with everyone?

Maybe a few people might even help out a bit!

Demo website hosted @ http://senchatouch2.firstfreight.com
usr: demo@example.com
pwd: demo

Setup should be as easy as:
	1) Clone git repository
	2) Setup WebServer & Database 
		i) IIS7 & MSSQL 2008
		ii) Anyone for other web/db servers? (hint, hint...)		
	3) Configure Mobile Website on WebServer
	4) Point your Phone/Tablet Browser & Go
	5) ** Create Step-By-Step Setup Guide / Screencast

To be Optimized for SmartPhones and Tablets

	1) Testing Devices: 
		IOS	    : iPhone | iPad
		Android : HTC Thunderbolt Phone | Motorola Zoom Tablet

	2) Software Components: 
		i)   Mobile Website 
		ii)  Web Server (ASP.NET Ajax/Json to MS SQL Server)

Project Goals (enough already with everyone having to re-create this wheel)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1) COMPLETE - 'Soup-to-Nuts' github project with all 'Standard Features' 
   in one easy to understand and well-documented project.

2) SIMPLE to clone & implement as the basis of an Enterprise Mobile App.

3) EASY and ACCESSIBLE to get started - without Googling, 
   forum posts, secret handshakes, cryptic tips, and stitching 
   together all the bits and pieces (as in: don't re-create the wheel).

4) COMMUNITY - Solicit and encourage input to provide a 'Best-Practices'
   Open-Source model for implementing a 'Rock-Solid' MVC Sencha Touch 2 project.

5) SUPPORT - How-to Guides (Blog posts), Screencasts & Documentation.

Data Storage
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	1) Encrypted Cookies	
	2) HTML5 LocalStorage 
	3) Device Native Storage (Contacts | Calendar | Email)
	4) Ajax Sync to DB Server

Bonus Features
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	1) Multi-Language
	2) Themeable
	3) Upload Company Logo

